# Test Admin Stats API

## Tạo test token admin
POST http://localhost:8800/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "your_admin_password"
}

## Test Music Sources Stats
GET http://localhost:8800/api/admin/stats/music-sources
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

## Test Top Contributors
GET http://localhost:8800/api/admin/stats/top-contributors  
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

## Test Songs Added
GET http://localhost:8800/api/admin/stats/songs-added
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

## Test User Growth
GET http://localhost:8800/api/admin/stats/user-growth
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

## Test All Stats Overview
GET http://localhost:8800/api/admin/stats/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}